data.description:
Seller offering contributions for a 2-1 BUY DOWN for buyer interest rate!! This 2 story townhouse has 4 bedrooms,  2.5  bathrooms  is centrally located between downtown Dallas and Rockwall and with almost instant access to 635 proves to be surprisingly charming.  Features such as 3 closets in the primary  bedroom, 2 balconies, a large picture window near the front entry, decorative moulding elements and a dramatic stone and dark wood corner fireplace and built-in bookcase makes a beautiful and bold statement.  Kitchen features  2 pantries and a terracotta tile backsplash, butcher block countertops and a cozy breakfast bar.  All bedrooms are upstairs and are fully carpeted with both bathrooms boasting solid surface countertops, sleek under mount sinks.  
Downstair floors have been replaced with Shaw LVP water resistant, new gutters, french doors installed
Foundation was inspected on 10-10-23, no repairs are needed
